# Calculates the aggregated uptake for peptide pool

This is a wrapper function for
[`calculate_aggregated_uptake`](https://hadexversum.github.io/HaDeX2/reference/calculate_aggregated_uptake.md),
which calculates aggregated uptake for only one time point. This
function returns values for all time points from \`kin_dat\`.

## Usage

``` r
create_aggregated_uptake_dataset(kin_dat)
```

## Arguments

- kin_dat:

  single state uptake data, product of e.q.
  [`create_uptake_dataset`](https://hadexversum.github.io/HaDeX2/reference/create_uptake_dataset.md)
